  "detailed_description": "ABOUT:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002590/extras/473181fbb480128623bde8f4bab9e6ab.gif?t=1694356449\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002590/extras/473181fbb480128623bde8f4bab9e6ab.poster.avif?t=1694356449\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br>N-GON is a vertical scroll shooter where you constantly face waves and waves of enemies. Dodge their attacks and fight them off. Kill them fast enough to get extra points.<br><br>MAGNET:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002590/extras/f1859dab519755b37a95cd88e38a3634.poster.avif?t=1694356449\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002590/extras/f1859dab519755b37a95cd88e38a3634.webm?t=1694356449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002590/extras/f1859dab519755b37a95cd88e38a3634.mp4?t=1694356449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Drop your bullet magnet to turn your enemies into big explosion chains. Some enemies a protected from direct attacks and need an indirect approach.<br><br>DIFFICULTY:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002590/extras/029486b6e18c9d8d79fcb500449ce895.poster.avif?t=1694356449\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002590/extras/029486b6e18c9d8d79fcb500449ce895.webm?t=1694356449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002590/extras/029486b6e18c9d8d79fcb500449ce895.mp4?t=1694356449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It starts slow, but soon it becomes impossible*.<br><br>SCORING SYSTEM:<br>Leaderboards are accessible for everyone. Start from any level all the way up to ENDLESS MODE, get the most out of score multipliers, become the best.<br><br>MISSIONS:<br>An integrated achievement system to track your progress across different tasks at hand.<br><br>UNLOCKABLES:<br>18 cosmetic cores, and 8 palettes. Unlockable alternative inverted color mode and a harder fast game mode.<br><br>FEATURES:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50 pre-designed levels<br></li><li>19 different enemy types, making for a lot of variety in terms of enemy combinations<br></li><li>special boss waves, where you face deadlier versions of enemies<br></li><li>ENDLESS MODE, a true challenge <br></li><li>Unique eye-melting art style</li></ul><br>------------------------------------<br>* it's not actually impossible",
