video></span><br>It starts slow, but soon it becomes impossible*.<br><br>SCORING SYSTEM:<br>Leaderboards are accessible for everyone. Start from any level all the way up to ENDLESS MODE, get the most out of score multipliers, become the best.<br><br>MISSIONS:<br>An integrated achievement system to track your progress across different tasks at hand.<br><br>UNLOCKABLES:<br>18 cosmetic cores, and 8 palettes. Unlockable alternative inverted color mode and a harder fast game mode.<br><br>FEATURES:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50 pre-designed levels<br></li><li>19 different enemy types, making for a lot of variety in terms of enemy combinations<br></li><li>special boss waves, where you face deadlier versions of enemies<br></li><li>ENDLESS MODE, a true challenge <br></li><li>Unique eye-melting art style</li></ul><br>------------------------------------<br>* it's not actually impossible",
